{"title":"EduNirbhar","markdown":{"yaml":{"title":"EduNirbhar","format":{"html":{"page-layout":"full"}}},"containsRefs":false,"markdown":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"home-page\">\n  <section class=\"hero-section\">\n    <div class=\"hero-content\">\n      \n      <h1>\n        EduNirbhar<br>\n        <em>One Stop Solution for Academicians</em>\n      </h1>\n      \n      <p class=\"hero-body\">\n        I provide specialized remote assistance to professors and researchers in  documentation, academic workflows etc. I also build fast, minimal websites for portfolios, research projects, and businesses.\n      </p>\n\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"home-page\">\n  \n    <h2 class=\"centered-title\">Why Choosing Us?</h2>\n    \n    <div class=\"glass-grid why-grid\">\n    \n  <div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n  <h4>Documentation Excellence</h4>\n  <p>Excel that computes flawlessly. Word docs that read like a professional wrote them. Decks that don't feel like clipart from 2003. No broken formulas. No formatting fights. Just clean, polished work — every time.</p>\n</div>  \n  \n   <div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n    <h4>Just You & Me</h4>\n    <p>No account managers. No junior staff. No offshore subcontractors. You email me, I do the work, you get the results. Simple. Consistent. Accountable.</p>\n  </div>\n  \n  <div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n    <h4>No Surprises, Ever</h4>\n    <p>Fixed price, upfront. Strict confidentiality, always. Your data stays private. Your budget stays predictable. Transparency isn't a perk here — it's the baseline.</p>\n  </div>\n  \n<div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n  <h4>Transparent Communication</h4>\n  <p>Real replies within 24 hours — not \"got it,\" an actual answer. Automatic updates at key milestones, so you never have to ask \"how's it going?\" Async-friendly, time-zone-proof. No ghosting. No chasing. No \"sorry for the delay\" three weeks later.</p>\n</div>\n  \n<div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n  <h4>Perfect, Or We Keep Going</h4>\n  <p>Unlimited revisions — genuinely unlimited. Not \"3 rounds then $50 a change.\" Deadlines are absolute: promised Friday 3 PM, delivered Friday 3 PM. Something's off? Fixed same day. Want a different approach? Done. No extra fees, no scope-creep debates, no guilt for asking. We're finished when you're satisfied — not when I decide we are.</p>\n</div>\n  \n  \n <div class=\"glass-card why-item\">\n  <h4>You Own Everything</h4>\n  <p>Every project ships fully commented and source-complete: .tex you can recompile, .qmd you can regenerate, .R and .py you can rerun on new data, .docx templates you can reuse, .xlsx models you can extend. No locked formats and watermarks. Update it yourself in minutes. Your files. Your control. Permanently.</p>\n</div>\n\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"trust-signals\">\n      <div class=\"trust-grid\">\n        \n        <div class=\"trust-stat\">\n          <div class=\"stat-num\">50+</div>\n          <div class=\"stat-label\">Projects Delivered</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"trust-stat\">\n          <div class=\"stat-num\">100%</div>\n          <div class=\"stat-label\">On-Time Delivery</div>\n        </div>\n        \n        <div class=\"trust-stat\">\n          <div class=\"stat-num\">&lt;24h</div>\n          <div class=\"stat-label\">Avg Response Time</div>\n        </div>\n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </section>\n  \n \n \n <section class=\"home-page\">\n  <h2 class=\"centered-title\">How we Work Together?</h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"uplift-stair-container\">\n    \n    <!-- Step 1 (Bottom Left - The Foundation) -->\n    <div class=\"uplift-step step-1\">\n      <div class=\"stair-text-top\">\n        <span class=\"stair-eyebrow\">Phase 01</span>\n        <h4>Share requirements</h4>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"stair-line\"><div class=\"stair-node\"></div></div>\n      <div class=\"stair-text-bottom\">\n        <p>Email or call with project details — type, deadline, and scope.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 2 (Middle - The Ascent) -->\n    <div class=\"uplift-step step-2\">\n      <div class=\"stair-text-top\">\n        <span class=\"stair-eyebrow\">Phase 02</span>\n        <h4>Align on scope</h4>\n      </div>\n      <!-- The explicit line with a joint node -->\n      <div class=\"stair-line\"><div class=\"stair-node\"></div></div>\n      <div class=\"stair-text-bottom\">\n        <p>Brief discussion to confirm deliverables and format to prevent rework.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- Step 3 (Top Right - The Summit) -->\n    <div class=\"uplift-step step-3\">\n      <div class=\"stair-text-top\">\n        <span class=\"stair-eyebrow\">Phase 03</span>\n        <h4>Deliver & Refine</h4>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"stair-line\"><div class=\"stair-node\"></div></div>\n      <div class=\"stair-text-bottom\">\n        <p>First draft for your feedback, then revision rounds until perfect.</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n \n \n\n  \n  <section class=\"section\">\n  <h2 class=\"centered-title\">Who Is EduNirbhar For?</h2>\n  \n  <div class=\"clean-tree-container\">\n    \n    <!-- ==========================================\n         TREE 1: ACADEMICIANS \n         ========================================== -->\n    <div class=\"tree-group\">\n      \n      <div class=\"tree-root\">\n        <div class=\"root-pill\">\n          <h3>Academicians</h3>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"tree-branches\">\n        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n          <div class=\"node-pill\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-graduation-cap\"></i>\n            <span>University Prof.</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n          <div class=\"node-pill\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-flask\"></i>\n            <span>Doctoral Fellows</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n          <div class=\"node-pill\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-book-open-reader\"></i>\n            <span>Academic Scholars</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <!-- ==========================================\n         TREE 2: FRESHERS / STUDENTS \n         ========================================== -->\n    <div class=\"tree-group\">\n      \n      <div class=\"tree-root\">\n        <div class=\"root-pill\">\n          <h3>Freshers / Students</h3>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n      \n      <div class=\"tree-branches\">\n        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n          <div class=\"node-pill\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-network-wired\"></i>\n            <span>Join as a Freelancer</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n        <div class=\"tree-node\">\n          <div class=\"node-pill\">\n            <i class=\"fa-solid fa-building-columns\"></i>\n            <span>AI & Tech Upskill</span>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n    \n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n<section class=\"content-section\">\n  <div class=\"wd-cta\">\n    \n    <h2>You deserve better<br>than \"good enough</h2>\n    \n  \n    <div class=\"hero-actions\">\n      <a href=\"/services/assistance.qmd\" class=\"btn-primary\">View Services ↗</a>\n      <a href=\"/learn/learn\" class=\"btn-ghost\">Explore Skills ↗</a>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n\n\n\n</div>\n```","srcMarkdownNoYaml":"\n\n```{=html}\n<div class=\"home-page\">\n  <section class=\"hero-section\">\n    <div class=\"hero-content\">\n      \n      <h1>\n        EduNirbhar<br>\n        <em>One Stop Solution for Academicians</em>\n      </h1>\n      \n      <p class=\"hero-body\">\n        I provide specialized remote assistance to professors and researchers in  documentation, academic workflows etc. I also build fast, minimal websites for portfolios, research projects, and businesses.\n      </p>\n\n  </section>\n  \n  \n  <section class=\"home-page\">\n  \n    <h2 class=\"centere